The girl used as a target to raise money for her sister: "If you think of a skin injury, you will be fine," - Xinhuanet.
A girl in Hangzhou Wulin Square stood in front of a large wooden board with the words "human flesh target, ten yuan and one arrow" written on the board.
Yesterday morning, a photo of a "Hangzhou girl willing to be a" target "to raise money for her sister" exploded in the circle of friends.
The photo shows a girl in Hangzhou Wulin Square standing in front of a large wooden board that is slightly taller than a person, with the words "human flesh target, ten yuan and one arrow" written on the board, indicating that passers-by can use a bow and arrow to shoot after payment.
This behavior aroused heated discussion among netizens.
Last night, the head of publicity at the Xiacheng Branch of the Hangzhou Public Security Bureau confirmed to the Beijing News reporter that the police confirmed that the girl had made such a drastic move to raise money for her sister, but this behavior was not worth advocating. After being warned, the girl left the local police station yesterday.
